08:28.250 --> 08:32.125
Cfaredo te thote shenjti ju duhet ta pranoni.

08:32.625 --> 08:37.792
Pra cilesia e pare qe Ganesha duhet te na jape eshte vinay "

08:38.083 --> 08:41.250
"vinay" do te thote perulje.

08:43.333 --> 08:47.667
